<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV39">
<l>nīlat taṭavarai mēṟpuṇṭa rīka neṭuntaṭaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>pōlap polintemak kellā viṭattavum poṅkumunnīr</l>
<l>ñālap pirāṉvicum pukkum pirāṉmaṟṟu nallōrpirāṉ</l>
<l>kōlaṅ kariya pirāṉem pirāṉkaṇṇiṉ kōlaṅkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Flourishing like long tanks of lotus on a broad</l>
<l>blue mountain for us they are in all places – the beauties</l>
<l>of our lord’s eyes: lord of the world [bordered by] the foaming sea,</l>
<l>the lord of the sky too, again the lord of good people, the lord black in colour.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
